                            <comment id="215185" author="jay" created="Sat, 2 Dec 2017 02:54:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9941&quot; title=&quot;lsm_is_composite() isn&amp;#39;t right&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9941&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9941&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="215183" author="jay" created="Sat, 2 Dec 2017 01:53:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Only b2_10 has such problem. The latest master seems good after FLR is landed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="215168" author="adilger" created="Fri, 1 Dec 2017 20:41:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Jinshan, now that FLR is landed, could you please take a look into this issue?  I suspect that something was broken with PFL and/or the file lease mechanism between 2.9 and 2.10, which is causing the migration to fail.  I saw similar problems with &lt;tt&gt;lfs migrate&lt;/tt&gt; with 2.10 clients and 2.7 servers.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
